text: Michael McCue (born March 19, 1993) is a Canadian professional squash player. As of June 2018, he was ranked number 93 in the world. He won his first world tour title at the 2018 Mount Royal University Open PSA5 tournament. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian male squash players Category:Sportspeople from Greater Sudbury
